{"tid":1258856,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"METAL BUILD EVA 2 號機拒賣給中國排隊黨！京都店「不懂日文的不賣」？","createTime":"2019-06-26T10:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T10:50:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1e289fe803e05fb7250c4c881915dfa94688c104","tid":1258856,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2385000/2385078/D90L29aU8AAToob_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2385000%2F2385078%2FD90L29aU8AAToob_1024.jpg&h=829fc6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前 BANDAI SPIRITS 推出的 Metal Build 新世紀福音戰士初號機大受歡迎，更引來排隊黨等炒賣問題。今次到 2 號機開訂，日本各大店舖同樣大排長龍，當中自然不乏排隊黨。有消息指京都 Yodobashi 電器店為了打擊炒賣，只會賣給日本人，不過店舖及後澄清，他們只是不賣給明顯是用來炒賣的人，而非所有外國人。<br />\n<br />\n稍早前在 Twitter 有日本網民表示，京都 Yodobashi 電器店要所有訂 Metal Build EVA 2 號機的顧客，要用日文說出商品名字，店舖才讓客人預訂，又指商品只賣給日本人，不會賣給外國人。日本網民得知消息後，不少人都讚好，紛紛表示支持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2385000/2385078/3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2385000%2F2385078%2F3_600.jpg&h=d05047d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過後來店方澄清，他們只是不賣給一批明顯用來炒賣的排隊黨，並非不賣給外國人，亦沒有歧視外國客人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2385078/METAL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2385078%2FMETAL&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmdC8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=ec5c975c\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2385078/METAL</a>"},{"pid":"5460cb67c0de852c6f2a82381c4bec74d27b1145","tid":1258856,"uid":79145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167dd8e31213b5634808